Parked my Rx7 outside of the house for 2 min and someone crashed right into it falling asleep behind the wheel. After repairing everything on the car, I take it to get an alignment and it mysteriously comes back from the shop barely running, later to found out the coolant seals were blown. I traded my MK4 Supra for this car and from the beginning it was a headache. Ended up taking a fat $10,000 loss on this one. Learn from mistakes! DM #BROKE 🥲
